FBIS4-55482 "dreeu095_i_94002" FBIS-EEU-94-095 Daily Report 16 May 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA Army: Serbs Fired on UN Position, Helicopter Army: Serbs Fired on UN Position, Helicopter LD1605212394 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network in Serbo-Croatian 2000 GMT 16 May 94 LD1605212394 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network Serbo-Croatian BFN [Text] A UNPROFOR [UN Protection Forces] position at the Brezovaca location on Mt Igman has come under heavy fire from the aggressor's positions. It ceased the moment the UN members responded accordingly. The chetniks also fired at a UN vehicle as it was passing along the Visoko-[word indistinct] road. Fire has also been opened at a UN helicopter overflying the (Vele) area, the 1st Corps says in its statement.
